'''uBlock Origin'''（发音''you-block''，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|j|uː|b|l|ɒ|k}}）是一款[[自由及开放源代码软件|自由、开源]]、[[跨平台|跨平台]]的[[内容过滤|内容过滤]][[浏览器扩展|浏览器扩展]]，包含广告屏蔽功能。此扩展可在多款浏览器上使用，包括[[Google_Chrome|Chrome]]、[[Microsoft_Edge|Edge]]、[[Firefox|Firefox]]、[[Opera電腦瀏覽器|Opera]]和[[Safari|Safari]] 13版本<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/chrisaljoudi/uBlock/issues/1544#issuecomment-150397875|title=Rebrand as Purify|accessdate=2015-10-25|archive-date=2017-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170425092310/https://github.com/chrisaljoudi/uBlock/issues/1544#issuecomment-150397875|dead-url=no}}</ref>之前。

uBlock Origin已获得多家技术网站的赞誉，其内存占用比其他同样功能的扩展更少。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://lifehacker.com/ublock-the-memory-friendly-ad-blocker-is-now-availabl-1681818949|title=uBlock, the Memory-Friendly Ad-Blocker, Is Now Available for Firefox|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2022-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220107040235/https://lifehacker.com/ublock-the-memory-friendly-ad-blocker-is-now-availabl-1681818949|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ghacks.net/2014/10/10/how-to-add-custom-filters-to-chrome-ad-blocking-extension-%C2%B5block/|title=How to add custom filters to Chrome ad-blocking extension µBlock|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2022-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220107041405/https://www.ghacks.net/2014/10/10/how-to-add-custom-filters-to-chrome-ad-blocking-extension-%c2%b5block/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/askjack/2015/jan/29/are-there-any-trustworthy-sources-for-downloading-software|title=Are there any trustworthy sources for downloading software?|accessdate=2015-02-17|archive-date=2022-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220107052156/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/askjack/2015/jan/29/are-there-any-trustworthy-sources-for-downloading-software|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.extremetech.com/computing/199188-%C2%B5block-aims-to-block-ads-without-draining-system-resources|title=µBlock aims to block ads without draining system resources|accessdate=2015-02-17|archive-date=2022-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105151538/https://www.extremetech.com/computing/199188-%c2%b5block-aims-to-block-ads-without-draining-system-resources|dead-url=no}}</ref>uBlock Origin的目标是为用户提供自行实施内容过滤的选择。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock|title=uBlock|accessdate=2015-02-27|publisher=GitHub|archive-date=2017-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170225131009/https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.idigitaltimes.com/adblock-plus-vs-ghostery-vs-ublock-origin-not-all-adblockers-were-created-equal-488257|title=Adblock Plus vs. Ghostery vs. Ublock Origin: Not All Adblockers Were Created Equal|last=Michael Gardiner|date=2015-11-05|publisher=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]|accessdate=2016-08-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160828195033/http://www.idigitaltimes.com/adblock-plus-vs-ghostery-vs-ublock-origin-not-all-adblockers-were-created-equal-488257|archivedate=2016-08-28}}</ref>

截至2021年，uBlock Origin继续由其创始人和主要开发者Raymond Hill积极开发和维护。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/graphs/contributors|title=Graph: contributors to gorhill/uBlock|accessdate=2016-08-01|archive-date=2019-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191214072224/https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/graphs/contributors|dead-url=no}}</ref>Hill援引“严重违背本项目的精神”撤出对该软件的旧分支“uBlock”的支持。此後，旧的分支也已不再被维护。<ref name="gorhill_readme">{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/blob/master/README.md|title=README|author=Raymond Hill|date=2015-08-16|access-date=2016-12-31|archive-date=2022-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220131120305/https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/blob/master/README.md|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
=== uBlock ===
[[File:Ublock_2015.svg|替代=uBlock Logo]]
uBlock Origin最初名为“μBlock”。名称后来被更改为“uBlock”以避免“µBlock”中“µ”的发音引致混乱。开发从基于{{tsl|en|HTTP Switchboard}}的[[代碼庫|代碼庫]][[分叉_(软件开发)|分支]]和另一个为高级用户设计的名为uMatrix的拦截扩展开始。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/gorhill/uMatrix|title=uMatrix - Github|access-date=2016-12-31|archive-date=2022-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220131120155/https://github.com/gorhill/uMatrix|dead-url=no}}</ref>uBlock是为利用社区维护的{{tsl|en|Blacklist (computing)|黑名單 (電腦)|黑名單}}（又稱為「屏蔽列表」）而开发，<ref name="brinkmann_chrome">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ghacks.net/2014/06/24/ublock-chrome-resource-friendly-adblocker-http-switchboard-author/|title=uBlock for Chrome is a resource-friendly adblocker by the HTTP Switchboard author|accessdate=2015-02-18|archive-date=2022-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105151528/https://www.ghacks.net/2014/06/24/ublock-chrome-resource-friendly-adblocker-http-switchboard-author/|dead-url=no}}</ref>同时增加功能和将[[软件质量|代码质量]]纳入到{{tsl|en|Release engineering|发布工程|发布}}标准。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/gorhill/uMatrix/wiki/Changes-from-HTTP-Switchboard|title=Changes from HTTP Switchboard|author=Raymond Hill|date=2015-05-12|access-date=2016-12-31|archive-date=2022-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105151532/https://github.com/gorhill/uMatrix/wiki/Changes-from-HTTP-Switchboard|dead-url=no}}</ref>

uBlock於2015年4月由最初的開發者Raymond Hill放棄並轉移給Chris Aljoudi<ref>{{cite web |url=https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/issues/38#issuecomment-91871802 |title=Please clarify uBlock₀ vs. uBlock |website=Github.com |first=Raymond |last=Hill |access-date=December 4, 2019 |archive-date=2022-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105184531/https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/issues/38#issuecomment-91871802 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，Hill自己分支一個專案回來維護並使用<ref>{{cite web |url=https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150427225211/https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/ |url-status=dead |archive-date=2015-04-27 |title=uBlock |date=April 27, 2015 |access-date=December 4, 2019 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這個版本後來改名為uBlock Origin，完全脫離了Aljoudi的uBlock<ref>{{cite web |url=https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/wiki/uBlock-Origin-is-completely-unrelated-to-the-web-site-ublock.org |title=uBlock Origin is completely unrelated to the web site ublock.org |last=Hill |first=Raymond |date=October 21, 2017 |website=GitHub.com |access-date=December 4, 2019 |archive-date=2022-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209170141/https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/wiki/uBlock-Origin-is-completely-unrelated-to-the-web-site-ublock.org |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在项目分裂后不久，Chris Aljoudi创建了ublock.org用以托管uBlock、宣传该扩展和请求捐助。對此，uBlock的创始人Raymond Hill表示“ublock.org所寻求的捐款不会使那些对uBlock Origin建立做出最大贡献的人受益。”<ref name="gorhill_readme">{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/blob/master/README.md|title=README|author=Raymond Hill|date=2015-08-16}}</ref>

该项目最后的源代码提交发生在2015年8月。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/chrisaljoudi/uBlock/commits/master|title=chrisaljoudi/uBlock|access-date=2016-12-31|archive-date=2017-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170425092250/https://github.com/chrisaljoudi/uBlock/commits/master|dead-url=no}}</ref>网站的安全证书已于2016年5月过期，并于2016年6月30日续订。2018年7月，uBlock被[[AdBlock|AdBlock]]開發商收購。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.ublock.org/announcement/|title=An update on uBlock|date=2018-07-13|work=ublock.org|access-date=2018-08-04|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105153210/https://ublock.org/announcement/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== uBlock Origin ===
[[File:UBlock_Origin.svg|替代=uBlock Origin Logo]]
Raymond Hill是uBlock的创始人和原始作者，它目前继续在名为uBlock Origin的扩展上工作，这有时被缩写（风格化）为「uBlock₀」。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ghacks.net/2015/04/25/official-ublock-origin-add-on-lands-for-firefox/|title=Official uBlock Origin add-on lands for Firefox|accessdate=2015-04-25|archive-date=2022-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105152226/http://www.ghacks.net/2015/04/25/official-ublock-origin-add-on-lands-for-firefox/|dead-url=no}}</ref>截至2016年12月，uBlock Origin Chrome擴充套件拥有700万活跃用户，Firefox版本有250万活跃用户。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/%C2%B5block/cjpalhdlnbpafiamejdnhcphjbkeiagm|title=uBlock Origin statistics|access-date=2016-12-31|archive-date=2015-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150129071629/https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/%C2%B5block/cjpalhdlnbpafiamejdnhcphjbkeiagm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://addons.mozilla.org/en-us/firefox/addon/ublock-origin/statistics/?last=30|title=uBlock Origin Firefox Statistics|access-date=2016-12-31|archive-date=2020-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200517082514/https://addons.mozilla.org/en-us/firefox/addon/ublock-origin/statistics/?last=30|dead-url=no}}</ref>

根據Sourcepoint与{{tsl|en|comScore}}的联合调查报告顯示，在截至2015年8月的10个月跟踪期内，它的增长率为833%，在已列出软件中增长最快。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://marketingland.com/heres-a-briefer-about-the-top-ad-blockers-146686|title=The Ad Blocker Landscape: What You Need To Know Today|accessdate=2015-10-17|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226190826/https://marketingland.com/heres-a-briefer-about-the-top-ad-blockers-146686|dead-url=no}}</ref>该报告将增长归因于用户对纯粹屏蔽软件的需求，而不想要有“[[Adblock_Plus|可接受广告]]”的程序。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.slideshare.net/sourcepoint/the-state-of-ad-blocking-september-2015?|title=The state of ad blocking - 2015年9月|accessdate=2015-10-17|publisher=Sourcepoint and comScore|archive-date=2022-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105151529/https://www.slideshare.net/sourcepoint/the-state-of-ad-blocking-september-2015|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年1月，uBlock Origin被加入到[[Debian|Debian]] 9和[[Ubuntu|Ubuntu]] 16.04的代码库<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://packages.debian.org/source/sid/ublock-origin|title=Debian Sid - uBlock Origin|accessdate=2016-01-21|archive-date=2022-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105152158/https://packages.debian.org/source/sid/ublock-origin|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/ublock-origin|title=Ubuntu - uBlock Origin|accessdate=2016-01-21|archive-date=2022-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105174627/https://launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/ublock-origin|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年5月，该扩展被Mozilla选为“本月精选”。<ref name="pickofmonth">{{Cite web|url=https://blog.mozilla.org/addons/2016/05/02/may-2016-featured-add-ons/|title=2016年5月 Featured Add-ons|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2022-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220107035536/https://blog.mozilla.org/addons/2016/05/02/may-2016-featured-add-ons/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Ellis Tsung (el1t)於2016年12月9日發布了用於[[Safari|MacOS Safari]]瀏覽器的uBlock Origin。<ref name="applesafari">{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/el1t/uBlock-Safari|title=uBlock Origin - An efficient blocker for Chromium, Firefox, and Safari. Fast and lean.|website=GitHub|language=en|accessdate=2017-10-12|archive-date=2022-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220127180059/https://github.com/el1t/uBlock-Safari|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Nik Rolls于2016年12月11日正式发布了用于[[Microsoft_Edge|微软Edge]]浏览器的uBlock Origin。<ref name="microsoftedge">{{Cite web|url=http://www.windowscentral.com/ublock-origin-available-microsoft-edge|title=uBlock Origin adblocker now available for Microsoft Edge via the Store|accessdate=2016-12-12|archive-date=2022-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105151527/https://www.windowscentral.com/ublock-origin-available-microsoft-edge|dead-url=no}}</ref>

此项目拒绝捐款。<ref name="gorhill_readme">{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/blob/master/README.md|title=README|author=Raymond Hill|date=2015-08-16}}</ref>

== 功能 ==

=== 屏蔽和过滤 ===
uBlock Origin和uBlock支持[[Adblock_Plus|Adblock Plus]]过滤规则的大多数语法，并包含Adblock Plus的订阅列表。流行的过滤规则列表[[Adblock_Plus|EasyList]]和EasyPrivacy是默认启用的订阅。该扩展还能导入[[hosts文件|hosts文件]]，以及安装一些社区提供的列表。在可用的hosts文件中，{{lang|en|Peter Lowe's Ad server list}}和{{lang|en|Malware Domains}}也被默认启用。一些额外功能包括：动态过滤脚本和[[HTML元素|iframe]]，一个隐藏网页元素的工具。截至0.8.7.0，uBlock中的动态过滤可以完全替代RequestPolicy或类似的附加组件。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/chrisaljoudi/uBlock/wiki/Dynamic-filtering|title=Dynamic filtering|author=chrisaljoudi|work=GitHub}}</ref>

uBlock Origin在日益成长中已包含多项uBlock没有的功能，例如：一种新的模式来帮助[[色盲|-{A]]，一个新的动态URL过滤功能，新的日志功能和增强接口：一个[[文档对象模型|DOM]]探查器、新的关注隐私的选项（阻止{{tsl|en|Link prefetching|链接预读}}、超链接审计和通过[[WebRTC|WebRTC]]泄露的IP地址）。各站点独立开关：切换[[弹出式广告|弹出窗口]]屏蔽、严格域屏蔽、美化规则、字体屏蔽。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/wiki|title=uBlock wiki|accessdate=2015-06-13|archive-date=2022-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220215185337/https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/wiki|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 性能 ===
技术网站和用户对uBlock的评论认为，该扩展相比提供类似功能的扩展（诸如Adblock Plus）占用更少的资源。<ref name="lynch_firefox">{{Cite web|url=http://jimlynch.com/internet/ublock-ad-blocker-added-to-mozillas-extensions-site/|title=uBlock ad blocker added to Mozilla’s extensions site|accessdate=2015-02-17|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150217142702/http://jimlynch.com/internet/ublock-ad-blocker-added-to-mozillas-extensions-site/|archivedate=2015-02-17}}</ref>2015年8月对十款屏蔽扩展进行的{{tsl|en|Benchmark (computing)|性能指标测试}}显示，uBlock Origin在测试扩展中能最有效率地利用资源。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.raymond.cc/blog/10-ad-blocking-extensions-tested-for-best-performance/view-all/|title=10 Ad Blocking Extensions Tested for Best Performance|accessdate=2015-08-26|archive-date=2022-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105152159/https://www.raymond.cc/blog/10-ad-blocking-extensions-tested-for-best-performance/view-all/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

uBlock会测探每个[[網頁|網頁]]所需的样式资源，而不是采用普适性的[[样式表|样式表]]。该扩展将用户启用的过滤规则创建一份[[快照_(電腦儲存)|快照]]。与每次都从缓存检索过滤规则相比，这有助于加快浏览器的启动速度。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/wiki/Notes-on-memory-benchmarks,-selfies|title=Notes on memory benchmarks, selfies|accessdate=2015-02-17|archive-date=2022-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209170254/https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/wiki/Notes-on-memory-benchmarks,-selfies|dead-url=no}}</ref>

